  Version bump. Bug #520284

  24 Jul 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  libgaminggear-0.2.0.ebuild, libgaminggear-0.3.0.ebuild:
  Remove virtual/udev dependency from 0.3.0 because libgaminggear-0.3.0.tar.bz2
  doesn't have a single reference to udev. Convert virtual/udev dependency to
  virtual/libgudev in 0.2.0 using := for automatic rebuild.

